      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle strikes an excellent balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, though close inspection reveals minor stone chipping on the front fascia and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows only light bolstering wear on the driver's side, while all power features, including the infotainment and climate control, operate exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, benefiting from a recent professional inspection, fresh fluid service, and a new set of high-performance tires. It tracks straight and provides a quiet, composed ride on the highway. This is a solid, honest example of a driver-focused car that has been cared for properly and is ready for immediate enjoyment.",
