      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound, driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit has been meticulously maintained with a documented VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the primary structural concerns of the chassis. The drivetrain remains tight, featuring a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. Performance is further sharpened by a Bilstein suspension refresh, providing improved damping profiles and reduced body roll without sacrificing street compliance. The exterior presents well with minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, while the interior leather maintains excellent bolster integrity. A turn-key enthusiast vehicle with all the critical preventative maintenance addressed.",
